          <li>Generated HTML table is invalid according to HTML5 specs <xref
              href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/issues/2095" scope="external" format="html">#2095</xref>
          </li>
          <li>Fix table and figure list to include number, title <xref
              href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/pull/2093" scope="external" format="html">#2093</xref>
          </li>
          <li>Remove obsolete info from codepage list <xref href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/pull/2091"
              scope="external" format="html">#2091</xref>
          </li>
          <li>Add axf.jar into log-processor taskdef classpath <xref href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/pull/2090"
              scope="external" format="html">#2090</xref>
          </li>
          <li>Add PFD2 index groups for a-breve, a-circ in Romanian <xref
              href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/pull/2081" scope="external" format="html">#2081</xref>
