            term and abbreviated-form DOTX058W) <xref href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/pull/1967"
              scope="external" format="html">#1967</xref>, <xref href="https://github.com/dita-ot/dita-ot/issues/1966"
              scope="external" format="html">#1966</xref>
